---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
---

<Base
  title="Engage — Global Faith Temple"
  description="Volunteer your time, offer a contribution, or partner with us. Quiet, faithful ways to walk with the temple."
>
  <main>

    <header class="relative bg-ivory pb-16 pt-40 md:pb-24 md:pt-48">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-6 text-center">
        <p class="fade-up mb-6 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.4em] text-olive opacity-80">Engage</p>
        <h1 class="fade-up font-serif text-4xl leading-[1.1] text-olive-deep md:text-6xl">
          Walk with us,<br />in your own way.
        </h1>
        <p class="fade-up mx-auto mt-8 max-w-2xl text-base leading-relaxed md:text-lg" style="color: rgba(43,42,29,0.78);">
          Our founder gave the whole of his life's work to begin this temple. What he asks of those who come after is no grand gesture — only a willingness to lend a hand, a gift, or a friendship to the long, gentle work of remembrance.
        </p>
        <div class="fade-up mt-12 flex items-center justify-center gap-3 text-olive opacity-50">
          <span class="h-px w-10" style="background: rgba(74,76,33,0.4);"></span>
          <svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 10 10"><circle cx="5" cy="5" r="1.4" fill="currentColor" /></svg>
          <span class="h-px w-10" style="background: rgba(74,76,33,0.4);"></span>
        </div>
        <nav class="fade-up mt-10 flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-x-6 gap-y-2 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-olive opacity-70">
          <a href="#volunteer" class="hover:text-olive">Volunteer</a><span class="opacity-30">·</span>
          <a href="#contributions" class="hover:text-olive">Contributions</a><span class="opacity-30">·</span>
          <a href="#partnerships" class="hover:text-olive">Partnerships</a>
        </nav>
      </div>
    </header>

    <!-- Volunteer -->
    <section id="volunteer" class="scroll-mt-24 border-t py-20 md:py-28" style="border-color: rgba(74,76,33,0.1);">
      <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-6xl gap-12 px-6 md:grid-cols-12">
        <div class="reveal-left md:col-span-4">
          <p class="mb-4 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-olive opacity-70">Volunteer</p>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl leading-tight text-olive-deep md:text-4xl">A few hours, given with care, become a great deal.</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="reveal-right md:col-span-8 space-y-5 text-[17px] leading-relaxed" style="color: rgba(43,42,29,0.82);">
          <p>
            Our volunteers are the steady hands behind every gathering, every meal, every quiet afternoon in the sanctuary. Many came first as visitors, and stayed because the work asked nothing of them but their honest attention.
          </p>
          <ul class="stagger mt-4 grid gap-3 sm:grid-cols-2">
            <li class="fade-up border-t pt-3" style="border-color: rgba(74,76,33,0.15); color: rgba(43,42,29,0.85);">— Sanctuary care &amp; welcome</li>
            <li class="fade-up border-t pt-3" style="border-color: rgba(74,76,33,0.15); color: rgba(43,42,29,0.85);">— Veterans' companionship &amp; visits</li>
            <li class="fade-up border-t pt-3" style="border-color: rgba(74,76,33,0.15); color: rgba(43,42,29,0.85);">— Meal preparation &amp; hospitality</li>
            <li class="fade-up border-t pt-3" style="border-color: rgba(74,76,33,0.15); color: rgba(43,42,29,0.85);">— Letter writing &amp; correspondence</li>
            <li class="fade-up border-t pt-3" style="border-color: rgba(74,76,33,0.15); color: rgba(43,42,29,0.85);">— Ceremony &amp; event support</li>
            <li class="fade-up border-t pt-3" style="border-color: rgba(74,76,33,0.15); color: rgba(43,42,29,0.85);">— Translation &amp; language exchange</li>
            <li class="fade-up border-t pt-3" style="border-color: rgba(74,76,33,0.15); color: rgba(43,42,29,0.85);">— Archive &amp; oral history work</li>
            <li class="fade-up border-t pt-3" style="border-color: rgba(74,76,33,0.15); color: rgba(43,42,29,0.85);">— Garden &amp; grounds keeping</li>
          </ul>
          <div class="mt-8">
            <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">Offer your time</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Contributions -->
    <section id="contributions" class="scroll-mt-24 border-t py-20 md:py-28" style="border-color: rgba(74,76,33,0.1); background-color: var(--parchment);">
      <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-6xl gap-12 px-6 md:grid-cols-12">
        <div class="reveal-left md:col-span-4">
          <p class="mb-4 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-olive opacity-70">Contributions</p>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl leading-tight text-olive-deep md:text-4xl">Gifts given quietly, used carefully.</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="reveal-right md:col-span-8 space-y-5 text-[17px] leading-relaxed" style="color: rgba(43,42,29,0.82);">
          <p>
            The temple was built without a single coin asked of the public — the founder gave it whole. What we ask now keeps the candle lit, the doors open, and the programs of remembrance and care alive for the families we serve. Every gift, of any size, is received with gratitude and stewarded with care.
          </p>
          <div class="stagger mt-6 grid gap-6 sm:grid-cols-3">
            <div class="fade-up border-l pl-5" style="border-color: rgba(74,76,33,0.3);">
              <p class="font-serif text-lg text-olive-deep">A steady gift</p>
              <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--muted-foreground);">A modest monthly offering that allows us to plan a year, and then another, with quiet confidence.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="fade-up border-l pl-5" style="border-color: rgba(74,76,33,0.3);">
              <p class="font-serif text-lg text-olive-deep">A single gift</p>
              <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--muted-foreground);">A one-time offering — large or small — given when the heart moves you, with no obligation to repeat.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="fade-up border-l pl-5" style="border-color: rgba(74,76,33,0.3);">
              <p class="font-serif text-lg text-olive-deep">In memoriam</p>
              <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--muted-foreground);">A gift in the name of someone you wish to honor. Their name is added to our roll of remembrance.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="mt-6 text-sm" style="color: var(--muted-foreground);">
            To make a contribution, please reach out through our
            <a href="/contact" class="text-olive underline-offset-4 hover:underline">contact page</a>.
            We will respond personally, and never resell or share your details.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Partnerships -->
    <section id="partnerships" class="scroll-mt-24 border-t py-20 md:py-28" style="border-color: rgba(74,76,33,0.1);">
      <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-6xl gap-12 px-6 md:grid-cols-12">
        <div class="reveal-left md:col-span-4">
          <p class="mb-4 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-olive opacity-70">Partnerships</p>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl leading-tight text-olive-deep md:text-4xl">Long friendships, patiently built.</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="reveal-right md:col-span-8 space-y-5 text-[17px] leading-relaxed" style="color: rgba(43,42,29,0.82);">
          <p>
            We welcome partnership with organizations whose work shares our values — peace, remembrance, and care across faiths and borders. The bond between Vietnam and her allies is renewed each time two communities sit down together with patience.
          </p>
          <div class="stagger mt-4 grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2">
            <div class="fade-up border-t pt-4" style="border-color: rgba(74,76,33,0.15);">
              <p class="font-serif text-base text-olive-deep">Communities of faith</p>
              <p class="mt-1 text-sm" style="color: var(--muted-foreground);">Shared liturgy, exchanges, and joint observances across traditions.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="fade-up border-t pt-4" style="border-color: rgba(74,76,33,0.15);">
              <p class="font-serif text-base text-olive-deep">Veterans' organizations</p>
              <p class="mt-1 text-sm" style="color: var(--muted-foreground);">Companionship, ceremonies, and remembrance work for the eight nations.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="fade-up border-t pt-4" style="border-color: rgba(74,76,33,0.15);">
              <p class="font-serif text-base text-olive-deep">Schools &amp; universities</p>
              <p class="mt-1 text-sm" style="color: var(--muted-foreground);">Study circles, scholarships, and oral history projects with the next generation.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="fade-up border-t pt-4" style="border-color: rgba(74,76,33,0.15);">
              <p class="font-serif text-base text-olive-deep">Cultural &amp; civic groups</p>
              <p class="mt-1 text-sm" style="color: var(--muted-foreground);">Concerts, exhibitions, and seasonal gatherings that honor a shared history.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-8">
            <a href="/contact" class="btn-ghost">Begin a conversation</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>
</Base>
